jobDescription: A 19-year old software engineer who loves to cook
aboutText: I am Aarnav Sanghvi, a 19-year old software engineer with a passion for learning new technologies and creating innovative solutions. I have experience in developing software applications in React, NextJS, and C++, and I have a strong understanding of development lifecycle processes. Additionally, I am an avid skier, reader, and podcast listener, which have all helped to shape my critical thinking and problem solving skills. I am eager to continue to develop my skillset and apply my knowledge of software development to create new and exciting projects.
